{
  "page": "Submission of Oldtown",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #1e90ff;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Mbox notice.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/40px-Mbox_notice.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/60px-Mbox_notice.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/80px-Mbox_notice.png 2x\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Note:</b> The title of this article is conjecture and may be subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Submission of Oldtown</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Faith_Militant_uprising\" title=\"Faith Militant uprising\">Faith Militant uprising</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/43_AC\" title=\"43 AC\">43&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a> victory\n</p>\n<ul><li>Submission of the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a> to the Iron Throne</li>\n<li>Crowning of <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Pater)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"High Septon (Pater)\">Septon Pater</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon\" title=\"High Septon\">High Septon</a></li>\n<li>Disbandment of the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_Militant\" title=\"Faith Militant\">Faith Militant</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Targaryen.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/30px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/45px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/60px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a></b><br /></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Star_of_the_Faith.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Star of the Faith.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/30px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/45px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/60px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 2x\" /></a><b><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/Faith_Militant\" title=\"Faith Militant\">Faith Militant</a></b>:\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/File:Warrior%27s_Sons.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Warrior&#39;s Sons.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/54/Warrior%27s_Sons.svg/20px-Warrior%27s_Sons.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/54/Warrior%27s_Sons.svg/30px-Warrior%27s_Sons.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/54/Warrior%27s_Sons.svg/40px-Warrior%27s_Sons.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Warrior%27s_Sons\" title=\"Warrior&#39;s Sons\">Warrior's Sons</a><br /></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Hightower.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Hightower.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/30px-House_Hightower.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/45px-House_Hightower.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/60px-House_Hightower.svg.png 2x\" /></a><b><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">House Hightower</a></b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/City_Watch_of_Oldtown\" title=\"City Watch of Oldtown\">City Watch of Oldtown</a></li></ul>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Order_of_the_Maesters\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Order of the Maesters\">Order of the Maesters</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a><br />Queen Dowager <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya_Targaryen\" title=\"Visenya Targaryen\">Visenya Targaryen</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Aenys_I)\" title=\"High Septon (Aenys I)\">High Septon</a>\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Morgan_Hightower\" title=\"Morgan Hightower\">Morgan Hightower</a></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Martyn_Hightower\" title=\"Martyn Hightower\">Martyn Hightower</a>\n</p>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Conclave\" title=\"Conclave\">Conclave</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">2 dragons:\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Vhagar\" title=\"Vhagar\">Vhagar</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Balerion\" title=\"Balerion\">Balerion</a></li></ul></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      200 Warrior's Sons\n<hr />\n<ul><li>Hightower knights</li>\n<li>1 reputed witch</li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">None</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      High Septon†\n<p>~ 50 Warrior's Sons\n</p>\n<hr />\nNone</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>In the year <a href=\"/index.php/43_AC\" title=\"43 AC\">43&#160;AC</a>, during the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_Militant_uprising\" title=\"Faith Militant uprising\">Faith Militant uprising</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> opened its gates to King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Prelude\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Prelude</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Suspects\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Suspects</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Aftermath\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aftermath</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prelude\">Prelude</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Submission_of_Oldtown&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Prelude\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>As a result of the defiance of many \"pious lords\", Dowager Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya_Targaryen\" title=\"Visenya Targaryen\">Viseyna</a> and King Maegor I <a href=\"/index.php/Burning_of_the_seats_of_the_pious_lords\" title=\"Burning of the seats of the pious lords\">burned</a> down their seats in the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a> with <a href=\"/index.php/Vhagar\" title=\"Vhagar\">Vhagar</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Balerion\" title=\"Balerion\">Balerion</a>, respectively. Then they turned south and flew to Oldtown, as the <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Aenys_I)\" title=\"High Septon (Aenys I)\">High Septon</a> had continued his denunciation against the King and had even issued a proclamation commanding the monarch to present himself before the <a href=\"/index.php/Starry_Sept\" title=\"Starry Sept\">Starry Sept</a> and beg the forgiveness of the gods.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Events\">Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Submission_of_Oldtown&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>As news of the impending arrival of two <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragons</a> reached the city, thousands fled through the city gates or taking ship. Thousands others took the streets and gave themselves over to drink and revelry, certain of their doom, or gathered at <a href=\"/index.php/Sept\" title=\"Sept\">septs</a>, temples and ancient woods to beg to the gods for their lives to be spared.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Within the Starry Sept, the High Septon prayed thunderously, calling upon the wrath of the Seven to fall down on <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>. Under the command of the Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Morgan_Hightower\" title=\"Morgan Hightower\">Morgan Hightower</a> two hundred <a href=\"/index.php/Warrior%27s_Sons\" title=\"Warrior&#39;s Sons\">Warrior's Sons</a> emerged from the city's chapterhouse and surrounded the seat of the Faith to defend His High Holiness.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Meanwhile the <a href=\"/index.php/Conclave\" title=\"Conclave\">Conclave</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Archmaesters\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Archmaesters\">archmaesters</a> met within the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a>, and the men of the <a href=\"/index.php/City_Watch_of_Oldtown\" title=\"City Watch of Oldtown\">City Watch</a> prepared to fight the fires, filling pails of water and sacks of sand. Along the city walls, defenses such as scorpions, spitfires were set up upon the battlements as well as crossbowmen and spearmen. Atop the <a href=\"/index.php/Hightower\" title=\"Hightower\">Hightower</a>, the beacon fire turned <a href=\"/index.php/Wildfire\" title=\"Wildfire\">green</a> to summon Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Martyn_Hightower\" title=\"Martyn Hightower\">Martyn Hightower</a>'s bannermen.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>As the sun was rising, <a href=\"/index.php/Vhagar\" title=\"Vhagar\">Vhagar</a>&#160;arrived, with <a href=\"/index.php/Balerion\" title=\"Balerion\">Balerion</a> joining at midday. However, the king found the city gates open, the battlements unmmaned, and the banners of Houses Targaryen, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">Tyrell</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">Hightower</a> flying atop the city walls. During the night, the High Septon, a robust man of three-and-fifty years and capable of preaching for a day and night without food or rest, had died under unknown circumstances.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After the news of the High Septon's death were known, Lord Martyn had sent his knights to disarm and take the Warrior's Sons captive. Hightower men were also sent to rouse the <a href=\"/index.php/Most_Devout\" title=\"Most Devout\">Most Devout</a> and march them to the Starry Sept at spearpoint to elect a new <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon\" title=\"High Septon\">High Septon</a>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Suspects\">Suspects</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Submission_of_Oldtown&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Suspects\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The causes for the death of the High Septon would be debated thereafter, and different causes would be argued:\n</p>\n<ul><li>The High Septon took his own life, either out of fear of Maegor's wroth or as a noble sacrifice to spare the people of Oldtown from <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonfire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dragonfire\">dragonfire</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>The Seven themselves struck him for his sins of pride, heresy, treason and arrogance.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser Morgan Hightower murdered him at the command of his lord brother. The knight had been seen entering and leaving the High Septons chambers during the night prior to the dragons' arrival.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Patrice_Hightower\" title=\"Patrice Hightower\">Patrice Hightower</a>, the maiden aunt of Lord Martyn and a reputed witch, is also a suspect, having sought an audience with His High Holiness at dusk, though he was seen alive when she departed.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Conclave\" title=\"Conclave\">Conclave</a>, either through the <a href=\"/index.php/Magic\" title=\"Magic\">dark arts</a>, an <a href=\"/index.php/Assassin\" title=\"Assassin\">assassin</a> or a <a href=\"/index.php/Poison\" title=\"Poison\">poisoned</a> scroll, as messages where exchanged between the Starry Sept and the Citadel during the night.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Queen Visenya Targaryen, on account of being a reputed sorceress.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Submission_of_Oldtown&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Pater)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"High Septon (Pater)\">Pater</a>, an amiable <a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">septon</a> of ninety years, blind, stooped and feeble was chosen as the new head of the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a>. The aged man, despite forgetting the words, eagerly blessed and annointed Maegor with holy oils.\n</p><p>The King would remain Oldtown for almost half the year, holding court and presiding trials. The captive Warrior's Sons were given the choice of taking the black or being executed. Three quarters of the knights chose the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a>. Of those who chose death, seven were beheaded by the king himself wielding <a href=\"/index.php/Blackfyre\" title=\"Blackfyre\">Blackfyre</a>, on account of their status as sons of lords or renowned knights; the rest were condemned to be decapitated by their own former brothers. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Morgan_Hightower\" title=\"Morgan Hightower\">Morgan Hightower</a>, meanwhile, was pardoned by Maegor.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After the executions, the High Septon announced the dissolution of both Warrior's Sons and <a href=\"/index.php/Poor_Fellows\" title=\"Poor Fellows\">Poor Fellows</a>, as the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a> would protect the Faith thereafter. King Maegor granted the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_Militant\" title=\"Faith Militant\">Faith Militant</a> until the end of the year to surrender their arms return to the <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_peace\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"King&#39;s peace\">king's peace</a>. Afterwards, the remaining rebels would be subject of a bounty: a gold dragon for the head of a Warrior's Son and a silver stag for the scalp of a Poor Fellow.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-12\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The king also reconciled with his first wife, <a href=\"/index.php/Ceryse_Hightower\" title=\"Ceryse Hightower\">Ceryse Hightower</a>, who agreed to accept the king's other wives, to honor and respect them, whilst she was restored to all her rights, incomes and privileges as wife and queen. A great feast, a bedding and a \"second consummation\" were held at the Hightower to celebrate the reconciliation.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-13\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Submission_of_Oldtown&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.00</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.01</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.02</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.03</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.04</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.05</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\">1.06</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\">1.07</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\">1.08</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\">1.09</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-10\">1.10</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-11\">1.11</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-12\">1.12</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-13\">1.13</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Sons of the Dragon.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Faith_Militant_uprising\" title=\"Template:Faith Militant uprising\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Faith_Militant_uprising&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Faith Militant uprising (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Faith_Militant_uprising&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nBattles of the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_Militant_uprising\" title=\"Faith Militant uprising\">Faith Militant uprising</a></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Burning_of_the_Sept_of_Remembrance\" title=\"Burning of the Sept of Remembrance\">Burning of th